com.bergerkiller.bukkit.tc.utils

Class LaunchFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bergerkiller.bukkit.tc.utils.LaunchFunction
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LaunchFunction.Bezier, LaunchFunction.Linear

    public abstract class LaunchFunction
extends java.lang.Object
    Algorithms for calculating a desired launched distance over time to launch from one velocity to another. Two modes can be used: fixed distance, or fixed time.
